此車站設有兩個[[側式月台|側式月台]]和三條軌道。中央軌道不營運<ref name="tracks">{{NYCS const|trackref|trackbook3}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/broadwayn/broadwayn6.jpg|title=Looking across to the narrow end of the windscreened Manhattan-bound platform|last=Cox|first=Jeremiah|date=May 26, 2010|website=subwaynut.com|access-date=August 8, 2017|archive-date=2017-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809092044/http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/broadwayn/broadwayn6.jpg|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此站在夾層設有狹窄的橫越道，容許乘客轉乘反方向列車<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/broadwayn/broadwayn16.jpg|title=Approaching the turnstiles from the Astoria-bound side, notice the sign for the narrow fenced in passageway to crossunder and change direction|last=Cox|first=Jeremiah|date=May 26, 2010|website=subwaynut.com|access-date=August 8, 2017|archive-date=2017-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809092009/http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/broadwayn/broadwayn16.jpg|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
=== 出口 ===
夾層配置如同[[30大道車站|30大道]]。付費區外的所有樓梯通過百老匯和31街的四個角落<ref name=maps>{{cite web|title=MTA Neighborhood Maps: Astoria|url=http://web.mta.info/maps/neighborhoods/qns/Q1_Astoria_2015.pdf|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=September 27, 2015|date=2015|archive-date=2018-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123153318/http://web.mta.info/maps/neighborhoods/qns/Q1_Astoria_2015.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/broadwayn/broadwayn18.jpg|title=A street level view of Broadway Station|last=Cox|first=Jeremiah|date=August 5, 2009|website=subwaynut.com|access-date=August 8, 2017|archive-date=2017-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809092019/http://www.subwaynut.com/bmt/broadwayn/broadwayn18.jpg|dead-url=no}}</ref> An exit-only stair from the northbound platform descends to the east side of 31st Street between Broadway and 34th Avenue.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://web.mta.info/mta/news/books/pdf/171113_1345_CPOC.pdf|title=Capital Program Oversight Committee Meeting|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=November 19, 2017|date=November 13, 2017|page=25|archive-date=2019-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823092914/http://web.mta.info/mta/news/books/pdf/171113_1345_CPOC.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

